oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session - RaeLynn with Nicolle Galyon - 2017-07-29
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by songwriters RaeLynn and Nicolle Galyon from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on July 29, 2017.
